61
00:03:40,455 --> 00:03:44,323
- Hey. Are you mad at me ?
- Amber Johnson ?

62
00:03:44,392 --> 00:03:47,555
Because it seemed like you
were mad at me. In the meeting.

63
00:03:47,628 --> 00:03:49,926
I'm just looking out for Naomi.
Hey. Amber.

64
00:03:51,032 --> 00:03:52,590
See you next week, Thomas.

65
00:03:52,667 --> 00:03:56,364
Addison is mad at me
because Cooper hired a stripper.

66
00:03:56,437 --> 00:03:59,600
I'm ignoring the stripper.
Today is a day for ignoring things.

67
00:03:59,707 --> 00:04:01,868
I am all business today.

68
00:04:01,976 --> 00:04:04,740
- Who's my next patient ?
- This guy wants to talk to you.

69
00:04:04,846 --> 00:04:07,007
Sign, please.

70
00:04:10,885 --> 00:04:13,217
- Oh, no.
- It's a nice bike.

71
00:04:14,956 --> 00:04:15,923
