72
00:04:21,896 --> 00:04:23,921
[Cooper] Emily's gained weight. Good.

73
00:04:23,998 --> 00:04:26,899
- Has she been sleeping ?
- Better. Don't you think ?

74
00:04:26,968 --> 00:04:28,526
No. I don't, actually.

75
00:04:31,038 --> 00:04:34,701
I said it was going to be a long haul
when she was born with these symptoms.

76
00:04:34,775 --> 00:04:37,437
I just feel like when is she
going to catch a break ?

77
00:04:37,512 --> 00:04:40,845
Well... Here you go.

78
00:04:40,915 --> 00:04:44,783
Come here, Emily.
Look at that guy. Where's that guy ?

79
